	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P78_is_identified_by> "He was the founder of the monastery of \n                  Zoz ʾAmbā in the Salāša district\n                  in Bagemdǝr. \n                  The chronology of his life is uncertain. At least one copy of \n                  Gadla ʾAbsādi of ʾAzazo \n                  is known to exist, but the text is still unpublished" .
